1. *Đubre* je najgori problem grada. (Garbage is the worst problem of the city.)
2. Beograd je preplavljen *đubretom*. (Belgrade is overwhelmed with garbage.)
3. Ljudi često bacaju *đubre* po ulicama. (People often throw garbage in the streets.)
4. Održavanje đubreta zahteva puno vremena i truda. (Maintaining garbage requires a lot of time and effort.)
5. Odloženo *đubre* smrdi. (The discarded garbage smells.)
6. Ne treba zanemariti zbrinjavanje *đubriva*. (The disposal of waste should not be neglected.)